{"tid":1314322,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭教學]物資人鏈：一隻手距離","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:35:42.000Z","uid":188428,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e26b260253fae54e579db5540e11a11b42e9be7","tid":1314322,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"抗爭現場，總不乏熱心人，<br />\n但大家要學識點樣有效運物資。<br />\n<br />\n口訣：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一隻手距離！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請同你身旁嘅人保持距離，<br />\n咁樣運物資會快好多！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBTiAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBTiAY.jpg&h=f63cde24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>錯誤示範：</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">企得太密，降低運輸效率</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0ENngg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0ENngg.jpg&h=8f8dcc75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2975c252550570c2f1d7ba7de5b9bd614af1f2a7","tid":1314322,"uid":188428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"[進階教學]<br />\n物資人鏈需要Coordinator<br />\n確保人鏈能達有價值的支援<br />\n<br />\nCoordinator的職責：<br />\n-設定人鏈的起點及終點<br />\n(物資點&lt;-&gt;前線的後排)<br />\n-保持人鏈keep住一隻手距離<br />\n-邀請示威者加入人鏈<br />\n<br />\nCoordinator可以找多幾個人<br />\n一起幫手管理人鏈"},{"pid":"d19bc1b88c404d3c03d2496c9b100ac59f1870a7","tid":1314322,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eeeb77d78327f58ecd08064f4e023bcf8e485ace","tid":1314322,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510815836f1651b54765674d7b0006c1979d35cc","tid":1314322,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"今日有進步<br />\n但都仲係逼咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：全日睇live"}]}